1. Enter the file name that is already present in the directory & Enter add & Enter data

File is already present in the directory so console asks user to add (or) overwrite. User entered add so now user entered data is added below the existing data.


2. Enter the file name that is already present in the directory & Enter overwrite & Enter data

File is already present in the directory so console asks user to add (or) overwrite. User entered overwrite so now user entered data is overwrite the existing data.

3. Enter the file name that is not present in the directory & Enter data

File is created. User entered data is written inside file.
